#: src/3614-project-goals.md:203
msgid ""
"There are a variety of planning processes around corporate goals. This "
"proposed goal process (6 month horizon, outcome-oriented, but qualitative "
"and not quantitative) is modeled on those processes but intentionally "
"simplified to account for Rust project needs."
msgstr ""

